                                java.util.List<Area2DGrid.ExpansionInfo.GridException<ObjectClass>> _objPlacement,

                                java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.util.HashSet<java.lang.String>> jointExceptions,
                                int width,

Creates a new instance of ExpansionInfo. Exception lists should be ordered in reverse order, only the first occurence for single WayPoint is used.

Parameters:
objInstancesInfo - Information about inherent objects. The Pair contains template needed to create the object and count of the objects
_kindExceptions - Exceptions of the "kind" member. As the default kind is used the parent's.
_objPlacement - Places for objects passed to sublocations
graphicTemplates - Exceptions of grpahic templates. The default value is in the next argument.
defaultTemplateStrings - Default graphic template.
width - Width of the grid
height - Height of the grid
